                "prose": "When the service is operational, its logs and any child resource\nlogs MUST NOT be accessible from the resource they record access\nto.\n"
              },
              {
                "class": "CCC.Core.C09",
                "id": "CCC.Core.C09.TR02",
                "name": "CCC.Core.C09.TR02",
                "parts": [
